    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Independent dollmakers who design and create one-of-a-kind dolls, their costumes, and other accessories, usually for individual sale to collectors.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
